en.11.4","text":"And they said, Go to, let us build us a city and a tower, whose top may reach unto heaven; and let us make us a name, lest we be scattered abroad upon the face of the whole earth.","year":-2247},{"id":"rec4jHwU9G7mJO5Gc","ref":"Gen.11.5","text":"And the LORD came down to see the city and the tower, which the children of men builded.","year":-2247},{"id":"reczWTm8IF3RW2RSI","ref":"Gen.11.6","text":"And the LORD said, Behold, the people is one, and they have all one language; and this they begin to do: and now nothing will be restrained from them, which they have imagined to do.","year":-2247},{"id":"recjKomlAk9rI3en4","ref":"Gen.11.7","text":"Go to, let us go down, and there confound their language, that they may not understand one another’s speech.","year":-2247},{"id":"recS6fO8Zcm4ThbSh","ref":"Gen.11.8","text":"So the LORD scattered them abroad from thence upon the face of all the earth: and they left off to build the city.","year":-2247}]}
